{"_type":"memory","key":"pdf-download-feature-pdf-download-20260618-uses-pdf","value":"PDF Download feature (pdf-download_20260618): Uses pdf-lib + @pdf-lib/fontkit for PDF generation. fontBytes is optional in translatedPdfGenerator (falls back to Helvetica). Font cached in IndexedDB via idb-keyval with key 'pdf-font:noto-sans:v1'. translateAllPages processes pages sequentially with per-page error isolation. usePdfDownload hook orchestrates 3-stage pipeline: translate-all → font fetch → PDF generation → browser download via anchor click. Noto Sans TTF fetched from fonts.gstatic.com with streaming progress. vi.stubGlobal returns previous value, not the spy — create vi.fn() separately."}
